      "contentHtml": "<p>Please visit the department's website to learn more about this major: <a href=\"http://www.femst.ucsb.edu\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">www.femst.ucsb.edu</a></p><p><br></p><p><strong>PREPARATION FOR THE MAJOR:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Area A: <strong>Introduction to Feminist Studies</strong>: Feminist Studies 20</p><p>Area B: <strong>Intersectionalities</strong>: Feminist Studies 60 and 80</p><p>Area C: <strong>Additional Key Concepts</strong>: Feminist Studies 30 or 40 or 50</p><p><br></p><p><em>(Transfer applicants do not need to complete all Preparation for the Major in order to be admitted, but should complete as much as possible before transferring so they will be prepared to progress in the major at UCSB.)</em></p>"
